definition: coin/money/CL:筆|笔[bi3]/unit of weight, one tenth of a tael 兩|两[liang3]

sentences.english: You ought to pay us the credit interest once payment is wrongly refused.
sentences.chinese: 若是拒付錯了，你們該當償付我方的銀行利錢。

sentences.english: You ought to pay us the prohilittlek interest once payment is wrongly refused.
sentences.chinese: 萬一拒付錯了，你們該當償付我方的銀行利錢。

sentences.english: You ought to pay us the prohiwhilek interest once payment is wrongly refused.
sentences.chinese: 萬一拒付錯了，你們應該償付我方的銀行利錢。

sentences.english: You ought to pay us the lender interest once payment is wrongly refused.
sentences.chinese: 倘使拒付錯了，你們應當償付我方的銀行利錢。

sentences.english: It helps to earn a little interest on your money.
sentences.chinese: 這可使你從放款中取得一點利錢。
